Package: biotaxa
Type: Package
Title: Visualising the growth and prediction of taxonomic diversity and identifying taxonomic incompleteness and imprecision
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Hsun-Yi Hsieh 
Maintainer: Hsun-Yi Hsieh <hhsunyi@naturalscience.be>
Description: This package visualise the accumulative curve of interested taxa over time, predicts taxonomic diversity and provides quantitative measures of taxonomic incompleteness and imprecision.
